import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from "@angular/common/http"; import { ItemViewModel } from './itemViewModel'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.scss'] }) export class AppComponent { public items: ItemViewModel[] = []; constructor(private http: HttpClient) { } public getItems() { this.http.get('https://localhost:7159/api/items').subscribe(x => { this.items = x; console.log(`got ${this.items.length} items`); }); } public clearItems() { this.items = []; } }
